<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="color-scheme" content="light dark">
    <title>数字原野 | 个人博客原型</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="stylesheet"
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:ital,opsz,wght@0,14..32,100..900;1,14..32,100..900&display=swap">
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #f8f9fa;
            --text: #121212;
            --accent: #e63946;
            --grid-gap: 2rem;
            --transition: 250ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            :root {
                --bg: #121212;
                --text: #f8f9fa;
            }
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "PingFang SC", sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        /* 布局系统 */
        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 5vw;
        }

        /* 导航 */
        nav {
            height: 100px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }

        .logo {
            font-weight: 900;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        /* 英雄区：Brockmann 风格非对称布局 */
        .hero {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
            gap: var(--grid-gap);
            margin-bottom: 8rem;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
            line-height: 0.9;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: -0.04em;
        }

        .hero-meta {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* 文章卡片：Rams 模块化风格 */
        .post-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 4rem;
        }

        .post-card {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            transition: var(--transition);
            border-top: 1px solid currentColor;
            padding-top: 1.5rem;
        }

        .post-card:hover {
            opacity: 0.7;
            transform: translateY(-8px);
        }

        .post-card img {
            width: 100%;
            aspect-ratio: 16/9;
            object-fit: cover;
            filter: grayscale(100%);
            transition: var(--transition);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .post-card:hover img {
            filter: grayscale(0%);
        }

        .post-card .category {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            color: var(--accent);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .post-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        /* 按钮与交互 */
        .btn-icon {
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border: 1px solid currentColor;
            background: transparent;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .btn-icon:hover {
            background: var(--text);
            color: var(--bg);
        }

        /* 响应式断点 */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .hero {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .hero-meta {
                border-left: none;
                border-top: 4px solid var(--accent);
                padding: 1.5rem 0 0 0;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .post-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container">
        <nav>
            <div class="logo">DIGITAL WILDERNESS.</div>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
                <button class="btn-icon" aria-label="Search"><i data-lucide="search"></i></button>
                <button class="btn-icon" aria-label="Menu"><i data-lucide="menu"></i></button>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <header class="hero">
            <h1>THINKING<br>OUT LOUD.</h1>
            <div class="hero-meta">
                <p>一个关于技术、设计与哲学的非线性个人博客。</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 2rem; opacity: 0.6;">EST. 2025</p>
            </div>
        </header>

        <main>
            <section class="post-grid">
                <a href="#" class="post-card">
                    <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/10/800/450" alt="文章配图">
                    <span class="category">Design Theory</span>
                    <h3>网格系统的秩序与背叛：从包豪斯到现代网页设计</h3>
                    <p>探索如何在严格的规则下寻找视觉的自由，以及为什么 1px 的偏差至关重要。</p>
                </a>

                <a href="#" class="post-card">
                    <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/48/800/450" alt="文章配图">
                    <span class="category">Technology</span>
                    <h3>后算法时代的个人书写：我们为什么还需要博客？</h3>
                    <p>在信息茧房中，个人博客是通往开放式互联网的最后一道出口。</p>
                </a>

                <a href="#" class="post-card">
                    <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/26/800/450" alt="文章配图">
                    <span class="category">Minimalism</span>
                    <h3>迪特·拉姆斯的设计十戒在 2025 年的实践</h3>
                    <p>好设计是诚实的。我们如何将这一原则应用到瞬息万变的代码世界中？</p>
                </a>
            </section>
        </main>

        <footer
            style="margin-top: 8rem; padding: 4rem 0; border-top: 1px solid currentColor; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end;">
            <div>
                <p>© 2025 DIGITAL WILDERNESS</p>
                <p style="opacity: 0.5;">DESIGNED WITH GRID SYSTEM</p>
            </div>
            <i data-lucide="arrow-up-right" style="width: 48px; height: 48px;"></i>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script>
        // 初始化图标
        lucide.createIcons();

        // 简单的入场动效
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.post-card');
            cards.forEach((card, index) => {
                card.style.opacity = '0';
                card.style.transform = 'translateY(20px)';
                setTimeout(() => {
                    card.style.transition = 'all 600ms cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1)';
                    card.style.opacity = '1';
                    card.style.transform = 'translateY(0)';
                }, index * 100);
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>